'''黃頤銘'''（{{lang-en|Edwyn Charles "Eddie" Huang}}，{{bd|1982年|3月1日}}）<ref name=FamilySearch-USPR-2009>{{cite web|title=Eddie Charles Huang - United States Public Records|url=https://familysearch.org/ark:/61903/1:1:QJ2V-LWZQ|website=FamilySearch|accessdate=2015-04-21|language=en|archive-date=2017-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318005954/https://familysearch.org/ark:/61903/1:1:QJ2V-LWZQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一位[[華裔|華裔]][https://gimy.tv/v_2534.html][[美國籍|美國籍]]餐館老闆、廚師、美食家、作家兼律師。<ref name=NYCourts-AttyDirectory-2009>{{cite web|title=Attorney Directory - Edwyn C. Huang|url=http://iapps.courts.state.ny.us/attorney/AttorneyDetails?attorneyId=330006967|website=New York State Unified Court System|accessdate=2015-04-21|language=en|archive-date=2017-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318200028/http://iapps.courts.state.ny.us/attorney/AttorneyDetails?attorneyId=330006967|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=reddit-IAmA-2013>{{cite web|last1=Huang|first1=Eddie|title=IAmA Eddie Huang (cook, author, host of Fresh Off the Boat)|url=https://www.reddit.com/r/IAmA/comments/174y57/iama_eddie_huang_cook_author_host_of_fresh_off|website=[[Reddit|Reddit]]|accessdate=2015-02-05|date=2013-01-23|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201042/https://www.reddit.com/r/IAmA/comments/174y57/iama_eddie_huang_cook_author_host_of_fresh_off|archivedate=2016-03-04|deadurl=no}}</ref>他是[[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]][[東村_(紐約市)|東村]]的[[刈包|刈包]]餐廳BaoHaus的老闆。<ref name=Time-XiaoYe-2011>{{cite news|last=Ozersky|first=Josh|url=http://www.time.com/time/nation/article/0,8599,2053195,00.html|title=Why Food Personality Eddie Huang Is Still Going Strong|work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]]|date=2011-02-23|accessdate=2014-03-01|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130824010613/http://www.time.com/time/nation/article/0%2C8599%2C2053195%2C00.html|archivedate=2013-08-24|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

== 早年生活 ==
黃頤銘生於[[美國|美國]][[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]]，其父親路易斯·黃（{{lang|en|Louis Huang}}）與母親潔西卡·黃（{{lang|en|Jessica Huang}}）皆為[[臺灣|臺灣]]移民。<ref name=NPR-FOtB-2013>{{cite news|last1=Martin|first1=Rachel|title='Fresh Off The Boat' And Serving Up Asian Culture|url=http://www.npr.org/2013/02/03/170556439/fresh-off-the-boat-and-serving-up-asian-culture|accessdate=2015-02-05|work=Weekend Edition|publisher=[[NPR|NPR]]|date=2013-01-29|format=Audio interview|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304063111/http://www.npr.org/2013/02/03/170556439/fresh-off-the-boat-and-serving-up-asian-culture|archivedate=2016-03-04|deadurl=no}}</ref>他從小在[[華府華埠|華府華埠]]長大，之後一家人搬往[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]][[奧蘭多_(佛羅里達州)|奧蘭多]]，其父親在那裡經營包含「大西洋灣海鮮燒烤餐廳」（{{lang|en|Atlantic Bay Seafood and Grill}}）及「牧牛人農場牛排館」（{{lang|en|Cattleman's Ranch Steakhouse}}）等數家相當成功的牛排與海鮮餐廳。<ref name=NYTimes-FOtB-review-2013>{{cite news|last=Garner|first=Dwight|title=Pork Buns Steamed in Bluster 'Fresh Off the Boat: A Memoir'|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/25/books/fresh-off-the-boat-a-memoir-by-eddie-huang.html?hpw|accessdate=2013-01-25|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2013-01-24|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229232254/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/25/books/fresh-off-the-boat-a-memoir-by-eddie-huang.html?hpw|archivedate=2014-12-29|deadurl=no}}</ref>他在年輕時便熱愛美國黑人文化，特別是[[嘻哈|嘻哈]]。<ref name=NYTimes-FOtB-review-2013/>他在成長過程中經常打架鬥毆，曾兩度因侵犯人身罪被捕。<ref name=PubWeekly-FOTB-2012>{{cite news|last1=Cutolo|first1=Ruby|title=Off The Boat, But On The Grid: PW Talks With Eddie Huang|url=http://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/authors/profiles/article/55130-off-the-boat-but-on-the-grid-pw-talks-with-eddie-huang.html|accessdate=2015-04-21|work=[[Publishers_Weekly|Publishers Weekly]]|date=2012-12-14|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314075207/http://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/authors/profiles/article/55130-off-the-boat-but-on-the-grid-pw-talks-with-eddie-huang.html|archivedate=2016-03-14|deadurl=no}}</ref>

黃頤銘在2000年進入[[匹茲堡大學|匹茲堡大學]]就讀，隔年轉學至[[羅林斯學院|羅林斯學院]]主修英文、輔修電影，並在2004年取得學士學位。<ref>{{cite news |last=Owen |first=Rob |url=http://communityvoices.post-gazette.com/arts-entertainment-living/tuned-in/item/38706-press-tour-former-pitt-student-slams-abc-sitcom-based-on-his-memoir-fresh-off-the-boat |title=PRESS TOUR: Former Pitt student Eddie Huang slams ABC sitcom based on his memoir, 'Fresh Off the Boat' |work=post-gazette.com |publisher=PG Publishing |date=2015-01-14 |accessdate=2016-04-20 |language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150512235301/http://communityvoices.post-gazette.com/arts-entertainment-living/tuned-in/item/38706-press-tour-former-pitt-student-slams-abc-sitcom-based-on-his-memoir-fresh-off-the-boat|archivedate=2015-05-12|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rollins.edu/magazine/archive/spring2009/profiles/huang.html |title=Eddie Huang '04 |last=Jackson |first=Ruth |publisher=Rollins College |accessdate=2016-04-20 |language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318210624/http://www.rollins.edu/magazine/archive/spring2009/profiles/huang.html|archivedate=2015-03-18|deadurl=no}}</ref>他在就讀羅林斯學院期間，曾獲頒芭芭拉·勞倫斯·阿爾方英文獎（{{lang|en|Barbara Lawrence Alfond English Award}}）及[[卓拉·尼爾·赫斯特|卓拉·尼爾·赫斯特]]獎，且是校刊《The Sandspur》的編輯。2008年，黃頤銘在[[葉史瓦大學|葉史瓦大學]][[班傑明·卡多佐法學院|班傑明·卡多佐法學院]]取得[[法律博士|法律博士]]學位。<ref name=NYPost-cf-Bourdain-2011>{{cite news|last1=Schuster|first1=Dana|title=Q&A: Six Seconds With... Eddie Huang is the new Anthony Bourdain|url=http://www.nypost.com/pagesixmag/issues/20110308/Eddie+Huang+new+Anthony+Bourdain|accessdate=2015-02-05|work=[[New_York_Post|New York Post]]|date=2011-03-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110314060722/http://www.nypost.com/pagesixmag/issues/20110308/Eddie%2BHuang%2Bnew%2BAnthony%2BBourdain|archivedate=2011-03-14|deadurl=yes|language=en}}</ref>卡多佐法學院期間，黃頤銘致力於[[清白專案|清白專案]]，擔任少數民族法律學生協會（{{lang|en|Minority Law Students Association}}）的會長，以及亞太裔美國人法律學生協會（{{lang|en|Asian Pacific American Law Students Association}}）的副會長，並曾在2006年獲得[[纽约市律师公会|纽约市律师公会]]的少數民族學生獎學金。<ref>{{cite web|first=James |last=Rickman|title=Eddie Huang and Jeezy on Racism, America and Bossing Up|work=PAPER Magazine|url=http://www.papermag.com/2015/04/eddie_huang_jeezy_fresh_off_the_boat.php|date=2015-04-27|accessdate=2016-04-22|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150812074926/http://www.papermag.com/2015/04/eddie_huang_jeezy_fresh_off_the_boat.php|archivedate=2015-08-12|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last=Huang |first1=Eddie |title=Fresh Off the Boat: A Memoir |publisher=Random House Publishing Group |year=2013 |page=211 |isbn=9780679644897 |accessdate=2016-04-22 |language=en}}</ref>

== 職業生涯 ==
黃頤銘初入職場的第一份工作是在[[紐約|紐約]]的{{le|查德本·派克律師事務所|Chadbourne & Parke}}擔任律師，主要負責[[公司法|公司法]]。他曾在2006及2007年擔任暑期實習生，之後在2008年被公司法部門聘用擔任正職。不到一年便發生了[[2007年–2008年環球金融危機|金融危機]]，黃頤銘因此被解僱，並開始表演[[獨角喜劇|獨角喜劇]]及擔任[[大麻|大麻]]販子。<ref name=NYTimes-Defies-Profile-2013>{{cite news|last=Stein|first=Joshua David|title=Chef Who Refuses to Be Defined by His Wok|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/24/fashion/eddie-huang-defies-description.html|accessdate=2013-01-26|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2013-01-23|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130124183539/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/24/fashion/eddie-huang-defies-description.html|archivedate=2013-01-24|deadurl=no}}</ref>

=== 服裝設計師 ===
2006至2009年間，黃頤銘經營一間名叫「胡德曼服飾」（{{lang|en|Hoodman Clothing}}）的街頭服飾公司，這間公司最初也被稱作「波道夫·胡德曼」（{{lang|en|Bergdorf Hoodman}}）。<ref name=UPROXX-Hoodman-2008>{{cite web|last1=TSS Crew|title=Hoodman Clothing|url=http://uproxx.com/smokingsection/2008/12/hoodman-clothing/|website=UPROXX|accessdate=2015-04-21|date=2008-12-01|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402141243/http://uproxx.com/smokingsection/2008/12/hoodman-clothing/|archivedate=2015-04-21|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name=SiliconPrairie-BigOmaha-Kaneko-2012>{{cite news|last1=Koch|first1=Macy|title=Eddie Huang: "I'm about getting paper, but I need a 'why'"|url=http://siliconprairienews.com/2012/05/eddie-huang-i-m-about-getting-paper-but-i-need-a-why/|accessdate=2015-04-21|work=Silicon Prairie News|date=2012-05-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402115023/http://siliconprairienews.com/2012/05/eddie-huang-i-m-about-getting-paper-but-i-need-a-why/|archivedate=2015-04-02|deadurl=no}}</ref>在此期間，他與一位在台灣認識的[[平面設計師|平面設計師]]寧·莊（{{lang|en|Ning Juang}}）合作設計衣服。<ref name=AllHipHop-Hoodman-2007>{{cite web|last1=Paine|first1=Jake|title=Hoodman Clothing: Politics as Usual|url=http://allhiphop.com/2007/06/20/hoodman-clothing-politics-as-usual/|website=AllHipHop|accessdate=2015-04-21|date=2007-06-20|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304105451/http://allhiphop.com/2007/06/20/hoodman-clothing-politics-as-usual/|archivedate=2016-03-04|deadurl=no}}</ref>

=== 廚師與餐館老闆 ===
黃頤銘從小在家看著媽媽做菜長大，因此對食物十分感興趣。他也向許多在他父親餐廳任職，具有不同文化背景及烹調風格的廚師學習烹飪技巧。他學習管理餐廳，以及如何成為一位好的「跑單員」（即餐廳中負責在前台與後台間傳遞資訊的人員），以確保出菜的順序及時間，盡可能高效率且快速地將最好的品質呈現給顧客。他從在奧蘭多地區開過數家餐廳的父親那，學得做為一位跑單員該有的技巧。<ref name=FoodRepublic-Bao-2011>{{cite news|last1=Nordee|first1=Emily|title=Talking With Eddie Huang: The bad-boy restaurateur takes a Bao|url=http://www.foodrepublic.com/2011/03/28/talking-eddie-huang|accessdate=2015-04-21|work=Food Republic|date=2011-03-28|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150512024551/http://www.foodrepublic.com/2011/03/28/talking-eddie-huang|archivedate=2015-05-12|deadurl=yes}}</ref>2011年，黃頤銘登上Chow.com年度美食界具影響力人物的Chow 13榜。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://eatocracy.cnn.com/2011/11/03/chow-13-honorees-a-sneak-peek/ |title=Chow 13 honorees - a sneak peek |work=CNN.com |publisher=Cable News Network |date=2011-11-03 |accessdate=2016-04-23 |language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001082323/http://eatocracy.cnn.com/2011/11/03/chow-13-honorees-a-sneak-peek/|archivedate=2015-10-01|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Birdsall |first=John |url=http://www.chowhound.com/food-news/95112/the-2011-chow-13/2/#wp_content |title=The 2011 CHOW 13 |work=Chowhound |publisher=CBS Interactive |date=2011-11-03 |accessdate=2016-04-23 |language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306100216/http://www.chowhound.com/food-news/95112/the-2011-chow-13/2/#wp_content|archivedate=2016-03-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>
