==== 餐廳 ====
2009年12月，黃頤銘在[[曼哈頓下城|曼哈頓下城]]的[[下東城|下東城]]成立一間[[台灣小吃|台式]][[割包|割包]]餐廳BaoHaus。<ref>{{cite news|last=Turner|first=David|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/culture/features/rap-snacks-inside-the-hip-hop-restaurant-boom-20151006|title= Rap Snacks: Inside the Hip-Hop Restaurant Boom|work= ''Rolling Stone''|date=2015-10-08|accessdate=2016-04-23|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408104254/http://www.rollingstone.com/culture/features/rap-snacks-inside-the-hip-hop-restaurant-boom-20151006|archivedate=2016-04-08|deadurl=no}}</ref>2011年7月，他將他的第一家店遷至[[東村_(紐約市)|東村]][[14街|14街]]238號，並且擴展菜單內容。<ref name=NYEater-Baohaus-2011>{{cite web|url=http://ny.eater.com/archives/2011/07/eddie_huang_opening_east_village_baohaus_this_month.php|title=Eddie Huang Opening East Village Location of BaoHaus|work=New York Eater|date=2011-07-14|accessdate=2014-03-01|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120322063536/http://ny.eater.com/archives/2011/07/eddie_huang_opening_east_village_baohaus_this_month.php|archivedate=2012-03-22|deadurl=no}}</ref>另一家餐廳「宵夜」（{{lang|en|Xiao Ye}}）卻沒有辦法複製BaoHaus的成功，並在販售[[Four_Loko|Four Loko]]的爭議下關門大吉。<ref name=NYObserver-XioYe-2015>{{cite news|last=Freeman|first=Nate|title=Xiao Ye, Eddie Huang's Bastion of Four Loko Has Shut Down|url=http://observer.com/2010/11/xiao-ye-eddie-huangs-bastion-of-four-loko-has-shut-down|date=2010-11-30|newspaper=The New York Observer|accessdate=2015-04-01|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308080428/http://observer.com/2010/11/xiao-ye-eddie-huangs-bastion-of-four-loko-has-shut-down/|archivedate=2016-03-08|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Yang |first=Wesley |url=http://cn.nytstyle.com/people/20150226/t26huang/ |title=《初來乍到》原型黃頤銘，打破亞裔模範迷思 |work=紐約時報中文網 |publisher=The New York Times |date=2015-02-08 |accessdate=2016-04-23 |language=zh-cn|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617024514/http://cn.nytstyle.com/people/20150226/t26huang/|archivedate=2015-06-17|deadurl=no}}</ref>

=== 作家 ===
黃頤銘創建了一個名為《初來乍到》（{{lang|en|''Fresh Off the Boat''}}）的部落格，之後由[[藍燈書屋|藍燈書屋]]出版了一本同名{{le|初來乍到：回憶錄|Fresh Off the Boat: A Memoir|回憶錄}}。<ref name=ThePopChef-FOtB-2012>{{cite web|url=http://thepopchef.blogspot.com|title=Fresh Off the Boat|work=The Pop Chef (blog)|date=2012-03-21|accessdate=2014-03-01|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309133537/http://thepopchef.blogspot.com/|archivedate=2014-03-09|deadurl=no}}</ref>《{{le|初來乍到：回憶錄|Fresh Off the Boat: A Memoir}}》於2013年初出版，獲得《[[出版者周刊|出版者周刊]]》<ref name=PubWkly-FOtB-review-2013>{{cite web|url=http://www.publishersweekly.com/978-0-679-64488-0|title=PW Pick: Fresh Off the Boat: A Memoir by Eddie Huang|work=[[Publishers_Weekly|Publishers Weekly]]|date=2013-01-29|accessdate=2014-03-01|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050923/http://www.publishersweekly.com/978-0-679-64488-0|archivedate=2016-03-04|deadurl=no}}</ref>及《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的好評。<ref name=NYTimes-Bestsellers-2013>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/best-sellers-books/2013-02-17/hardcover-nonfiction/list.html|title=Best Sellers|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2013-02-27|accessdate=2014-03-01|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305175316/http://www.nytimes.com/best-sellers-books/2013-02-17/hardcover-nonfiction/list.html|archivedate=2016-03-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>

=== 電視節目 ===
黃頤銘曾在2011年底主持{{le|烹飪頻道|Cooking Channel}}的《廉價美食》節目，也上過幾集《{{le|獨家美食|Unique Eats}}》。之後，他離開烹飪頻道，為《[[Vice_(雜誌)|Vice]]》主持《初來乍到》節目，隨後更名為《{{link-en|黃的世界|Huang's World}}》（{{lang|en|''Huang's World''}}）。<ref name=NYTimes-FOtB-review-2013 /><ref name=HighSnobiety-HuangsWorld-2014>{{cite web|url=http://www.highsnobiety.com/2014/08/02/eddie-huang-to-premiere-huangs-world-on-munchies|title=Eddie Huang to Premiere 'Huang's World' on MUNCHIES|last1=Banks|first1=Alec|date=2014-08-02|website=Highsnobiety|accessdate=2014-11-06|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307103607/http://www.highsnobiety.com/2014/08/02/eddie-huang-to-premiere-huangs-world-on-munchies/|archivedate=2016-03-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>

==== 《-{|zh-tw:菜鳥新移民;zh-hans:初来乍到}-》 ====
2014年，[[美國廣播公司|美國廣播公司]]基於他的著作製作了一齣電視劇《-{|zh-tw:[[菜鳥新移民|菜鳥新移民]];zh-hans:[[初来乍到|初来乍到]]}-》，由[[藍道爾·朴|藍道爾·朴]]及[[吳恬敏|吳恬敏]]主演，[[楊昇德|楊昇德]]飾演黃頤銘。<ref name=WaPo-FOtB-2015>{{cite news|last1=McDonald|first1=Soraya Nadia|title=Meet Eddie Huang, the memoirist who inspired 'Fresh Off the Boat'|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/02/04/meet-eddie-huang-the-memoirist-who-inspired-fresh-off-the-boat/|accessdate=2015-02-05|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=2015-02-04|language=en}}</ref>2015年2月4日，這齣劇率先播出兩集預告，並於2月10日的[[黃金時段|黃金時段]]首映。<ref name=NYTimes-Mag-FOtB-2015>{{cite news|last1=Yang|first1=Wesley|title=Eddie Huang Against the World|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/02/08/magazine/eddie-huang-against-the-world.html?_r=0|accessdate=2015-02-05|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2015-02-03|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150205022833/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/02/08/magazine/eddie-huang-against-the-world.html?_r=0|archivedate=2015-02-05|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name=appledaily-2015>{{cite news|author=林奐成|title=台裔刈包小子 奮鬥史拍美劇|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20150116/36330484/|accessdate=2016-04-24|work=[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]]|publisher=[[壹傳媒|壹傳媒]]|date=2015-01-16|language=zh-tw|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150119080510/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20150116/36330484/|archivedate=2015-01-19|deadurl=no}}</ref>

