==爭議==

===TED夥伴===
2012年，黃頤銘成為2013年[[TED大會|TED]]夥伴計畫的一員。<ref name=NYTimes-Defies-Profile-2013/>後來，根據夥伴協議，他因為沒有參加大會的任何一場活動，使其夥伴身分被廢除。<ref name=The-Verge-Inside-ted-thesmartest-bubble-in-the-world>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2013/3/5/4061684/inside-ted-the-smartest-bubble-in-the-world|title=Inside TED: the smartest bubble in the world |publisher=The Verge |date=2013-03-05 |accessdate=2015-07-18|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307230142/http://www.theverge.com/2013/3/5/4061684/inside-ted-the-smartest-bubble-in-the-world|archivedate=2016-03-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>他更將TED形容為「[[山達基|山達基]][[夏令營|夏令營]]」。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://heavy.com/social/2013/09/ted-conference-exposed-summer-camp-huang/|title=Apparently, Doing a TED Talk is Like Being Trapped at 'Scientology Summer Camp'|first=Danny |last=Vega|publisher=Heavy.com|date=2013-09-19|accessdate=2016-04-24|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219010449/http://www.heavy.com/social/2013/09/ted-conference-exposed-summer-camp-huang|archivedate=2014-02-19|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name=PoliticalBlindspot-TED-2013>{{cite web|url=http://politicalblindspot.com/eddie-huang-says-ted-conferences-have-turned-into-a-scientology-cult-video|title=Eddie Huang Says TED Conferences Have Turned Into A "Scientology Cult" (video)|publisher=Political Blind Spot|date=2013-06-24|accessdate=2014-03-01|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320005051/http://politicalblindspot.com/eddie-huang-says-ted-conferences-have-turned-into-a-scientology-cult-video/|archivedate=2016-03-20|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

===黑人婦女言論===
2015年5月，黃頤銘在《[[馬赫脱口秀|馬赫脱口秀]]》發表有關黑人婦女的言論引發批評。他說：「在美國，我認為亞裔的男子氣概一直被過度弱化，基本上，我們被看作是黑人婦女一般。」隨後，他利用自己的[[Twitter|Twitter]]帳號@MrEddieHuang與@BlackGirlDanger交流，並對自己的言論被看作是{{le|厭黑人女性症|Misogynoir|仇視黑人女性}}作辯解。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Chu|first1=Arthur|title=Eddie Huang self-destructs: Why the "Fresh Off the Boat" author's descent into misogyny is so depressing|url=http://www.salon.com/2015/05/15/eddie_huang_self_destructs_why_the_fresh_off_the_boat_authors_descent_into_misogyny_is_so_depressing_partner/|work=Salon|date=2015-05-15|accessdate=2015-05-15|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314170832/http://www.salon.com/2015/05/15/eddie_huang_self_destructs_why_the_fresh_off_the_boat_authors_descent_into_misogyny_is_so_depressing_partner/|archivedate=2016-03-14|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Ting|first1=Jenevieve|title=We Need to Talk About Eddie Huang's Misogyny|url=http://msmagazine.com/blog/2015/05/11/we-need-to-talk-about-eddie-huangs-misogyny/|work=Ms.|date=2015-05-11|accessdate=2015-05-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150913142331/http://msmagazine.com/blog/2015/05/11/we-need-to-talk-about-eddie-huangs-misogyny/|archivedate=2015-09-13|deadurl=no}}</ref>

===唱美國國歌笑場===
2017年黃頤銘在美國麻州錄製<<黃的世界>>，應邀於美國業餘球隊Yarmouth–Dennis Red Sox主場唱美國國歌，由於在唱國歌時因為緊張頻頻笑場，導致唱完美國國歌後與現場主辦單位白人發生嚴重口角，被指責唱歌嬉笑不尊重美國國歌，黃頤銘極力澄清他不是專業歌手已努力演唱並無藐視之義，但還是當場被主辦單位以髒話怒罵趕出球場。

